Class TicTacAI

  • public class TicTacAI
extends java.lang.Object
    Compilation: javac TicTacAI.java Dependencies: java.util.Random

    The TicTacAI class takes in a tic tac toe table in the form of a two dimensional char array and adds a move to it based on its state and the selected difficulty. To see its implementation go to Heroku - Tic Tac Toe.
